[normal]The following was submitted via the committee's website online application form, if I've missed anything, I'm sure it will be covered by one of the numerous other 
[normal]knowledgeable submissions
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]This is the submission by 
[normal]Cyclox
[normal] of Oxford, for measures that would help safer cycling.   It covers cycle training, enforcement of regulations, infrastructure and planning.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Planning requirements for cycle parking provision at residential/business developm
[normal]ents are enforced. For people to feel able to use their bikes, they need to be confident there will be a secure parking place at their destination to help prevent theft of their cycle. One quarter of those who have a cycle stolen give up cycling and don't 
[normal]replace their cycle.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]January 2014
